
                             THE LEADING FORCE
      
                                 SKID ROW

                              Present to you

                       Pinball Dreams  (Prerelease)

 Short Dox.

 Press F1 starts one player game
 or *ENTER* on keypad add new players, upto 8 players are possible.

 Press "P" pauses the game , and if you press "ESC" while in pause mode,
 you can abort the game.

 To restart game quickly after game over sequence press "F10"

 Press "M" for Music on/off.

 CONTROL KEYS:

  left  flipper: L. CBM Amiga or L. shift or L alt. 
  right flipper: R. CBM Amiga or R. shift or R alt. 

  to pull trigger , press the key "arrow key down",
  or pull mouse back and release with left mouse!


THIS GAME WAS CONVERTED TO A FULLY PLAYABLE ONE STAGE GAME BY BLACKHAWK/SR

